<SiteLayout
  site="westmount"
  title="Best Canadian Bond ETFs in 2026: ZAG, VAB, XBB Compared"
  description="A comprehensive guide to the best Canadian bond ETFs, comparing aggregate and short-term options like ZAG, VAB, and XBB."
